strings: <voice_0x01000BE5><se_def>China: ... we are convinced of that. You can talk again now.
<voice_0x01000BE6><se_low>King of tricks: What happened to AIDS? What on earth are you going to do to me!
<voice_0x01000BE7><se_def>China: Like I said, I'm sorry that I didn't lie about the ring. Maybe Marcelo will beat me!
<voice_0x01000BE8><se_def>China: If they saw me, I'd have nowhere to go. But I'm here for you, okay?
<voice_0x01000BE9><se_def>China: Follow me and don't be angry! But I'm going to show you something you haven't seen yet.
<voice_0x01000BEA><se_low>King of tricks: what do you think?
<voice_0x01000BEB><se_def>China: These bumps were dyed with blood.
<voice_0x01000BEC><se_def>China: If I throw you to the ground and close the door, you'll get stabbed.
<voice_0x01000BED><se_def>China: My hands are dirtier and emptier than yours, is that not bad?
<voice_0x01000BF1><se_low>King of tricks: <Cap><hero> Did you see from the side? There is a hidden passage inside!
